<h2>Independent Study (Supervisor: Shao-I Chu)</h2>
<p>Application of Reinforcement Learning Based on Image Processing in the Side-Scrolling Action Game 《Hollow Knight》</p>
<p>Related Video Introduction:</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
    <iframe width="800" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EeooyhH2kHc" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div>

<h3>Project Image Gallery</h3>
<div class="image-gallery">
    <div class="image-item">
        <img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/By5-nPaBJx.png" alt="Image 1" class="project-image" />
    </div>
    <div class="image-item">
        <img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ryvYsPpHkg.png" alt="Image 2" class="project-image" />
